title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters dialog
description: When creating multiple report parameters and setting default values for them, the default values are not being displayed in the Show Report Parameters dialog. This occurs after dragging the parameters to the layout.
OB: The default values of the report parameters are not visible in the Show Report Parameters dialog after dragging the parameters to the layout.
EB: The default values of the report parameters should be displayed in the Show Report Parameters dialog after dragging the parameters to the layout.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Create multiple report parameters.
2. Set default values for these parameters.
3. Drag the parameters to the layout.
4. Open the Show Report Parameters dialog.

Expected result:
The default values of the report parameters should be shown in the Show Report Parameters dialog.

Observed result:
The default values of the report parameters are not visible in the Show Report Parameters dialog after dragging the parameters to the layout.
